  "title": "AB03 - Operations Manager (Catering Services)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Catering Operations Manager</strong></p><p>Work Days: 5 days (including weekends)</p><p>Salary: $4,300 to $4,900</p><p>Address: Sembawang</p><p><u><strong>Job responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Work closely with operations, sales and kitchen team to ensure the clients’ needs are met</li><li>Oversee and monitor all operations and logistics for all catering events</li><li>Manage manpower planning to suit different catering needs</li><li>Monitor service, food and beverage standards and resolve any issues if necessary</li><li>Build and maintain good working relationship with clients and handle customer complaints</li><li>Monitor and maintain vehicle standard, food quality, service standard & smooth running of the catering office and central kitchen</li><li>Understanding with and complying with the mandatory hygiene standards and requirements</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least 5 year(s) of working experience in catering line or hotel catering services</li><li>Possess Diploma/GCE ‘A’ or ‘O’ Level</li><li>Willing to work shifts, weekends and public holidays</li><li>Class 3 driving license </li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
